metadata.dc:description: The Work is a study of quality voice in laryngectomy patients with speech prosthetic supports. We have studied the quality voice objective and subjective. We explain the results.
metadata.dc:title: Estudio de la calidad de la voz en laringuectomizados con prótesis fonatoria.
[Voice quality in laryngectomees with phonatory prosthesis].
